title: Welcome to Virginia
description:
The second album by The Bluegrass Cardinals, Welcome to Virginia was released on LP in 1977 and has never been re-released. This is a digital recording from the 39-year old LP.

Track listing:

1 Roll on Muddy River

2 She Keeps Hanging On

3 Journey to My Savior's Side

4 Lorene

5 We Know the Man

6 Darling Corey

7 Ridin' on the L & N

8 Blue Eyed Boston Boy

9 Plant Some Flowers

10 Darcey Farrow

11 Jesus, Lead Me Evermore

12 Mississippi River Man
